{"tid":1574090,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"\b前線FA立場問題","createTime":"2019-09-16T09:21:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T00:27:00.000Z","uid":263015,"like":59,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"a5aab480c098417ff356fae2eab46b12f37194db","tid":1574090,"uid":263015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T09:21:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n琴日開始有好多巴打問FA應唔應該救藍屍<br />\n我可以好肯定答你 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>理論上係應該要救</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\nFA主張嘅係<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">人道救援精神</span></span></strong><br />\n人道救援係指無論對方嘅身份 性別 年齡 種族 政見<br />\n只要現場環境許可 理應上係要盡救<br />\n所以好多FA都要係救人方面保持中立 而避免偏頗任何一邊<br />\n呢個先係FA嘅專業精神<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nAnyway，<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>光復香港 時代革命</strong></span></span><br />\n香港人加油 無論你係勇武定係和理非定係文宣都好 手足們要萬事小心<br />\n我愛大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c8e1f01fb16853a64c8f3b81346cbcc472434e1","tid":1574090,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T09:22:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pvsTHEi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpvsTHEi.jpg&h=e8bfe3ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">宣佈 和你suck 4.0 9月22 星期日見<br />\n<br />\nsuck 4.0 將會基於 hkmap.live 行動  <br />\n麻煩力推呢個livemap <br />\n對各位日後行動都非常大幫助<br />\n<br />\n請各位必須係 9月22日當日12點30分留意channel / 連登 / IG 最新消息<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連登post:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568754\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568754</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br